{"tid":2373490,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有個傻仔上fb買海味俾人呃","createTime":"2021-01-20T13:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T06:33:31.000Z","uid":160584,"like":29,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6691ef037495f7ae2208339bbbb9eb203456b4","tid":2373490,"uid":160584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"無錯，俾人呃個個就係家母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事關家母上fb見到good product有個po <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0WstSr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0WstSr.jpg&h=363e7e65&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n啲瑤柱好似好靚又抵就payme落單買，俾錢就緊係無問題啦 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDvtdjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDvtdjw.jpg&h=228a14e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\npay完$298 俾埋資料話今日12點前送貨，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jFdpsS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jFdpsS.jpg&h=74949fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係家母今日等左成日都無聲氣就覺得比人呃左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nInbox無人覆 俾人blk埋，就確定係俾人呃啦。<br />\n見佢個po有成千個cm都幾多反應，想睇下有無同路人都俾條仆街呃左，同埋睇下可以點解決。$298唔係多，但都係錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾，屌你老母，老人家錢都呃祝你早日仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再上fb買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be00a9c3a357324a8924cb597eed0072fc9a3e25","tid":2373490,"uid":277186,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:18:17.000Z","msg":"叫老母去報警先，唔通比班死黑警hea"},{"pid":"ef0c5d52a1015679aff733ceaa10a8b7c54e0de7","tid":2373490,"uid":26071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:18:38.000Z","msg":"都要去報狗"},{"pid":"fd562f5ba39eabbdda363fd65ee94ccb521190c1","tid":2373490,"uid":254711,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"ci